original_title: Musk considers backing Vance instead of starting a third party — WSJ  — The Donald
article_summary: Elon Musk is considering supporting JD Vance, a former Democrat, for political office, due to connections with Peter Thiel and Vivek Ramaswamy, Vance's college roommate. The discussion stems from Vance's personal life, including his marriage to an Indian woman and the names of his children.</s>
